ExCuSe pupil detector
=====================

Algorithm and original source: Wolfgang Fuhl, Thiago C. Kübler, Klaus
Sippel, Wolfgang Rosenstiel, Enkelejda Kasneci, University of Tübingen.

Reference: Fuhl, W., Kübler, T., Sippel, K., Rosenstiel, W., Kasneci, E.
(2015). "ExCuSe: Robust Pupil Detection in Real-World Scenarios."
*CAIP 2015*, 39-51.

